{{Infobox book |image = 50 reasons people give for believing in a god.JPG |author = [[Guy P. Harrison]] |name = 50 reasons people give for believing in a god |country = United States |language = English |subject = [[Religion]] |publisher = [[Prometheus Books]] |release_date = 2008 |media_type = [[paperback]], |isbn = 978-1-59102-567-2 |dewey = |congress = |oclc = |pages = 354 }}
'''''50 reasons people give for believing in a god''''' is a 2008 book by journalist [[Guy P. Harrison]]. It was his first book. The book examines fifty common reasons that believers across the world give for believing in a god. It draws on his conversations with people while traveling both for business and pleasure in 20 years as a journalist. Harrison notes that very few people are interested in the complex arguments that go on between theologians and atheists. The people he has talked with say they believe because that is what their parents taught them, and their parents wouldn't lie to them, or because that is what it says in their book of wisdom. Of the 50 reasons, Harrison concludes that the most common reasons people believe are because it is just obvious to them, because everyone is religious so it must be true, or because it brings them happiness.<ref> Point of Inquiry [http://www.pointofinquiry.org/guy_p_harrison_50_reasons_people_give_for_believing_in_a_god/ August 1, 2008 Guy P. Harrison - 50 Reasons People Give For Believing In A God] Retrieved August 15, 2017</ref> Harrison takes a calm and empathetic attitude towards people who believe, in contrast to some other atheist works.<ref> Patheos.com [http://www.patheos.com/blogs/friendlyatheist/2008/06/20/book-review-50-reasons-people-give-for-believing-in-a-god-by-guy-p-harrison/ June 20, 2008 Book Review: 50 Reasons People Give for Believing in a God by Guy P. Harrison] Retrieved August 27, 2015 </ref> He describes [[Richard Dawkins]]' use of the term "faith heads" to describe believers as "a lot like an insult" and writes that it is "counterproductive."<ref> {{cite book |last= Harrison|first= Guy P.|date= 2008|title= 50 reasons people give for believing in a god|publisher= [[Prometheus Books]]|page= 155|isbn=978-1-59102-567-2}} </ref>
